<BlogLayout
  title="Crossword Game Notation Explained — How to Read and Write Scrabble Game Records"
  description="Learn Crossword Game Notation (CGN) — the standard format for recording Scrabble games. Understand coordinates, play format, exchanges, challenges, and passes."
